(16, 'vi', 'KHÁM PHÁ CHÂU ĐỐC                     (1 ngày)', NULL, '<p>cập nhật</p>', '<p>cập nhật</p>', '1 Day', '30 USD / 1 người', 'boat, car', 'Floating fish farm -Visit Cham minority village, the weavings shop-- Sam muontain and pagoda village, Cam Mountain, Tuc Dup hill'),
(16, 'en', 'AROUND CHAU DOC (1 DAY)', NULL, '<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small; color: #0000ff;">First we take a ride cruising to <strong>floating village</strong> (fish farm) and <strong>Cham minority village</strong> for visiting a weaving workshop of the colorful traditional wears (Sarong and towels).</span></p>', '<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">First we take a ride cruising to <strong>floating village</strong> (fish farm) and <strong>Cham minority village</strong> for visiting a weaving workshop of the colorful traditional wears (Sarong and towels).</span></p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Back to Chau Doc for a visit to<strong> Chua Xu Lady''s temple</strong> and <strong>Cave pagoda</strong> at the foot of Sam&rsquo;s mountain.</span></p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">The next destination will be <strong>Cam mountain</strong>- the highest mountain in Mekong delta. On the way there, you can enjoy sightseeing the two rice fields along the road, or drop by for a short visit to a small <strong>Khmer village</strong>. Your mind will be cleaned by sightseeing nothing from the empty of the rice field and the sky!&nbsp; You will have a short walk up on the mountain side to see the daily life of mountain people.</span></p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Have lunch on the way (on the guests&rsquo; budget).</span></p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>Tuc Dup </strong>(the two million dollar hill) is a bold strewn hill deep in the Mekong delta where between late 1968 and early 1969 against overwhelming odds. The defenders&nbsp; kept the full force of the&nbsp; American army at bay for 128 days&nbsp; of continuous bombardment, two million is said to be the cost of the firepower the American used in their vain attempt to capture this isolated stronghold.</span></p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Explore freely around hidden caves interconnected by a labyrinth of natural tunnels and paths, under ground meeting rooms, hospital, living quarters, stores and command H.Q. (most fully restored).</span></p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Back for <strong>Sam&rsquo;s mountain</strong> to admire the grand view of Mekong Delta from the top of Sam&rsquo;s mountain and the sunset on Cambodia side.</span></p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">End the tour at Chau Doc.</span></p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\n<div style="text-align: justify;">\n<table border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="443">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width="91">\n<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>NO.</strong></span></p>\n</td>\n<td width="176" valign="top">\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>01 pax </strong>(Usd/ pax)</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width="176" valign="top">\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>02 pax </strong>(Usd/ pax)<strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width="91">\n<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>PRICE<br /> <em>(by Motor)</em></strong></span></p>\n</td>\n<td width="176" valign="top">\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>$30</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\n</td>\n<td width="176" valign="top">\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>$25</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width="91">\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>PRICE<br /> <em>(by Car)</em></strong></span></p>\n</td>\n<td width="176" valign="top">\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>$55</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\n</td>\n<td width="176" valign="top">\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>$35</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\n<table border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width="310" valign="top">\n<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>All program Tour service Includes:</strong></span></p>\n</td>\n<td width="310" valign="top">\n<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>All   program Tour service Not Includes:</strong></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width="310" valign="top">\n<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">- English Speaking guide</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">- Admission fee to indicted sights</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">- Boat trip as stated in above sights</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">- All transfers<strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\n</td>\n<td width="310">\n<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">- Meals &amp; drinks</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">- Personal expense and others not stated</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">- Bike to the peak to Sam&rsquo;s mountain.<strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>', '1 day', '30 USD / 1 person', 'Boat, car', 'Floating fish farm -Visit Cham minority village, the weavings shop-- Sam muontain and pagoda village, Cam Mountain, Tuc Dup hill'),
(15, 'en', 'Uninhabited Phu Quoc - Discover the North Island', NULL, '<p>Those who''ve been to Phu Quoc - paradise of sea, certainly will not  forget the moments on the ocean, the same mix blue water, watching the  colorful coral reefs are blessed or along with the crew to experience  the lives of fishermen on the island. Besides the fun when the sentence  was the uncle of grouper, red fish ... it was a peaceful moment, a quiet  inside the white sandy beach with pristine inherent definition. Travel  Journey to Green - Green Cruise Tourism, will never forget those moments  that Green Journey Travel will send tourists ...</p>', '<div>\n<div>\n<div style="background-color: #009900; height: 16px; padding: 3px 5px; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #0000ff; font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: small; color: #ffffff;">07h30</span><br /></span></div>\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="background-color: #ffffff; font-size: xx-small; font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span></div>\n<div style="text-align: justify;">\n<p>Vehicles and tour guides taking tourists visiting the barrel of fish  sauce, fish learn traditional brewing methods to create the flavor of  Phu Quoc fish sauce is famous. Guests can buy fish sauce in the shop.</p>\n</div>\n<div>\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: small; font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; color: #0000ff;"><em><br /></em></span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div style="background-color: #009900; height: 16px; padding: 3px 5px; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #0000ff; font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: small; color: #ffffff;">8h30</span><br /></span></div>\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="background-color: #ffffff; font-size: xx-small; font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span></div>\n<div style="text-align: justify;">\n<p>The statue garden tour, learn the traditional methods of pepper to  create a special category of targets in the island. Guests can purchase  targets in the garden.</p>\n</div>\n<div>\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: small; font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; color: #0000ff;"><em><br /></em></span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div style="background-color: #009900; height: 16px; padding: 3px 5px; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #0000ff; font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: small; color: #ffffff;">10h00</span><br /></span></div>\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="background-color: #ffffff; font-size: xx-small; font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span></div>\n<div style="text-align: justify;">\n<p>Car to the visitors section of the ecological reserve Oil: Hiking and  exploring primeval forest. The nose section of oil in visitors can watch  sea border of Cambodia and simple life experience of local fishermen,  enjoy fresh seafood here (self expense tourists pay).</p>\n</div>\n<div>\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: small; font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; color: #0000ff;"><em><br /></em></span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div style="background-color: #009900; height: 16px; padding: 3px 5px; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #0000ff; font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: small; color: #ffffff;">12h00</span><br /></span></div>\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="background-color: #ffffff; font-size: xx-small; font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span></div>\n<p>Then the car takes visitors to beaches, Surround yourself with ocean and  white sand beaches of the BBC in 10 votes is a wild and beautiful  beaches in the world.</p>\n<div>\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: small; font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; color: #0000ff;"><em><br /></em></span></p>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div style="background-color: #009900; height: 16px; padding: 3px 5px; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #0000ff; font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: small; color: #ffffff;">14h00</span><br /></span></div>\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="background-color: #ffffff; font-size: xx-small; font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span></div>\n<p>Travelers returning to the town of Duong Dong, sightseeing Dinh Cau, a  symbol of the fishermen on the island and visit the wine production  facilities sim famous Phu Quoc.</p>\n<div>\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: small; font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; color: #0000ff;"><em><br /></em></span></p>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div style="background-color: #009900; height: 16px; padding: 3px 5px; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #0000ff; font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: small; color: #ffffff;">15h00</span><br /></span></div>\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="background-color: #ffffff; font-size: xx-small; font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span></div>\n<p>Vehicles bring tourists back to the hotel to rest and free activities.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', '7h30', '100 USD / 1 person', 'Car Tours, High Speed Vessel', 'Barrel house Khu Tuong pepper sauce'),
